1157
01:11:51,850 --> 01:11:53,240
Bahkan M3gan sekalipun.

1158
01:11:54,240 --> 01:11:55,930
Bibi ikut sedih.

1159
01:11:56,130 --> 01:11:58,250
Mestinya bibi cerita padamu
